Package: birmrssim
Title: Simulation Tests for the Beta Item Response Model with Response Styles (BIRM-RS).
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Anonym", "Anonym", , "a.nonym", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Anonym Anonym <a.nonym@test.com>
Description: This package evaluates parameter recovery in the Beta Item Response Model with Response Styles (BIRM-RS). It simulates data using the BIRM-RS, fits the model to the simulated data, and includes a wide range of customizable simulation conditions, such as sample size and number of items. 
